room_title: Escape room "Bomb Squad" by Dells Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
room_description: Wisconsin Dells Police Department has discovered a suspicious case in the alley behind 325 Broadway. Your elite squad of bomb technicians has been called to the scene to investigate and defuse the item in question. Your captain has reason to believe this is a time-sensitive issue. It is up to your team to disarm the bomb and save all the tourists.
